<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4982618>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1A–E. Pseudepitettix convexa Deng, sp. nov., holotype female. A—body, lateral view; B—the same, dorsal view; C—head and anterior part of pronotum, dorsal view; D—the same, lateral view; E—head, frontal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4982618/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4982634>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4A–L. P. nigritibis Zheng & Jiang, 2000; P. linaoshanensis Liang & Jiang, 2004; P. torulosinota (Zheng & Lin, 2016); P. guibeiensis Zheng & Jiang, 1995; P. pimkarnae Storozhenko & Dawwrueng, 2014; P. yunnanensis Zheng, 1995. A—P. nigritibis, dorsal view of body; B—P. nigritibis, lateral view of body; C—P. linaoshanensis, lateral view of body; D—P. linaoshanensis, dorsal view of body; E—P. torulosinota, dorsal view of body; F—P. torulosinota, lateral view of body; G—P. guibeiensis, dorsal view of body; H—P. guibeiensis, lateral view of body; I—P. pimkarnae, dorsal view of body; J—P. pimkarnae, lateral view of body; K—P. yunnanensis, dorsal view of body; L—P. yunnanensis, lateral view of head and pronotum.(A–B photo: Weian Deng, C–D after Liang & Jiang, E–F photo: Zheng & Lin, G–H after Zheng & Jiang, I–J photo: Storozhenko & Dawwrueng, K–L after Zheng)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4982634/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4982636>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5A–D. P. strictivertex Deng, 2020; P. hainanensis Deng, 2020. A—P. strictivertex, dorsal view of body; B—P. strictivertex, lateral view of body; C—P. hainanensis, dorsal view of body; D—P. hainanensis, lateral view of body. (A–D photo: Weian Deng)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4982636/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

